{"tid":1468194,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地需要團結 取得共識！","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:57:36.000Z","uid":41342,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"33b05ee607d665e8a65fce56e73c14d8d8421d8b","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:10.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會old news<br />\n黑警仆街無底的線 唔代表我地無底線<br />\n一直以黎維持我地走到呢步既係巿民既支持<br />\n<br />\n今晚行動大家可能有啲說話甚至指責<br />\n與其指責 不如指點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3e27KH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3e27KH3.png&h=1d594b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖好好既示範展示我地應該點做 有咩唔可以做<br />\n（我知有特事特辦 但大前提下我地要有自限）<br />\n<br />\n想各位俾啲idea出黎<br />\n抗爭有咩係我地既底線  請列出原因<br />\n因為有啲大爭議  如：塞鐵、佔旺等等<br />\n要講出原因同做法  等有事既時候可以即時應對<br />\n<br />\n我唔知咁做會唔會俾人話我地有組織咁去行動<br />\n（我其實好多野都唔知 好多野都最壞情況諗 希望幫到大家brain storming)"},{"pid":"5f85e0d3fa25a40a9297db3ef1d47cbb8ceb3293","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc309a00792689136a8db569d8a449b1e45d6ce4","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:52.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"0028b4ac3335b3c1e833821f3fd192cc2150e0fd","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:03.000Z","msg":"727"},{"pid":"d0f06be1c5975995d0038414d471d312ced6a89e","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"63f898e5fd2006a36da9afca294488b248304d02","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"200m+1+5"},{"pid":"a3570ed4ab8d9a93d8ab0ed2f41d2ee9d733aef4","tid":1468194,"uid":41342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:47.000Z","msg":"777dl